{"tid":1421732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬未來可以用到嘅恐怖戰術","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:31:14.000Z","uid":182792,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0fae63dadc88b9999b06c72668df198e2c39a8cf","tid":1421732,"uid":182792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"而家有好多所謂<span style=\"color: red;\">刀手準備打示威者啦</span><br />\n剩係琴日都有兩單<br />\n兩邊我地都有反撃<br />\n荃灣仲打到個人爆缸<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但留意到好多人唔知咩事  見到人打佢又打咁</span><br />\n仲分別打左兩輪<br />\n雖然嗰個人都真係抵打<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係班狗其實都混左好多鬼入黎示威者呢邊<br />\n如果喺追打刀手嗰時<br />\n集鬼先出手真係打一個路過無辜嘅人   之後其他示威者又圍埋去一齊打<br />\n就會造成係示威者無差別攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家真係要fact check左先打埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27352077d907ae0b15fbbf4d8e3d51dcefa6873","tid":1421732,"uid":182792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eab2bf90da10acd46bd42e98b2042467fd743b3","tid":1421732,"uid":167928,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"係連登仔唔記得中共滲透最勁 唔肯信前線有鬼"},{"pid":"f8cc98633d7b52777fe33d355f497b271f543639","tid":1421732,"uid":182792,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4eab2bf90da10acd46bd42e98b2042467fd743b3","tid":1421732,"uid":167928,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"係連登仔唔記得中共滲透最勁 唔肯信前線有鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"前線有鬼就緊<br />\n但亦都唔可以唔相信前線<br />\n所以大家要喺信前線之餘有自己嘅個人意志<br />\n唔好人做佢又做"},{"pid":"d769b926823c0